data.description: Finish what they started! This home has had some work done but has a little left to go. Not afraid of some drywall needs or paint? Then this is your gem to make your own.  This home had a new roof installed in 2014 and the rest is now cosmetic. This 4 bedroom 2.5 bathroom home features a 2 car garage, opened up lower floor plan, GREAT family room upstairs, and work done to update the bathrooms.  This is one of those "it has great bones" moments you have been looking for (but with not all the work needed).  This home is being offered as-is. Don't forget to look around this desirable Elmwood Park location, blocks from all the shopping and dining it offers! This is a great place for any family with easy access to schools and the nature preserve.  Please feel free to reach out with any questions. Thanks for looking at our listing.
